Skins.Name: Wandering Traveler
Skins.BgDescription: Rover's usual outfit. This is what she wore at the beginning of her journey and what she will be wearing for the rest of it.

Skills.SkillDescribe:
Basic Attack

Rover-Havoc performs up to 5 consecutive attacks, dealing Havoc DMG.


Heavy Attack

Rover-Havoc consumes STA to attack, dealing Havoc DMG.
Use Basic Attack after casting Heavy Attack to cast Basic Attack 4.


Mid-air Attack

Rover-Havoc consumes STA to cast a Mid-Air Plunging Attack, dealing Havoc DMG.


Dodge Counter

Use Basic Attack after a successful Dodge to attack the target, dealing Havoc DMG.
Transform sound into feathers, dealing Havoc DMG.
Rover gathers resonating sounds to attack targets, dealing Havoc DMG.
In the Dark Surge state, gain 20% Havoc DMG Bonus.
While in the Dark Surge state, Basic Attack recovers 1 extra Resonance Energy when it hits a target. This effect can be triggered 1 time per second.
Attack the target, dealing Havoc DMG.

Devastation

When "Umbra" is full, hold Basic Attack to cast Devastation to attack the target, dealing Havoc DMG, considered as Heavy Attack DMG.


Dark Surge

After casting Devastation, Rover enters the Dark Surge state. In this state:
-Basic Attack is replaced with Enhanced Basic Attack, which performs up to 5 consecutive attacks, dealing Havoc DMG.
-Heavy Attack is replaced with Enhanced Heavy Attack;
-Use Basic Attack after casting Enhanced Heavy Attack to cast Heavy Attack Thwackblade to attack the target, dealing Havoc DMG, considered as Heavy Attack DMG.
-Use Basic Attack after casting Heavy Attack Thwackblade to cast Enhanced Basic Attack 3 to attack the target, dealing Havoc DMG;
-Resonance Skill Wingblade is replaced with Resonance Skill Lifetaker, transforming sounds into blades to attack the target, dealing Havoc DMG.


Umbra

Rover can hold up to 100 points of Umbra.
Normal Attack Tuneslayer recovers Umbra on hit.
Resonance Skill Wingblade recovers Umbra when cast.
Resonance Skill Lifetaker recovers Umbra when cast.
Intro Skill Instant of Annihilation recovers Umbra when cast.
Rover summons a Havoc Field, dealing Havoc DMG of 143.3% of Rover's ATK to all targets within the range every 2s for 6s.

ResonantChain.AttributesDescription: Resonance Skill DMG Bonus is increased by 30%.
Reset Resonance Skill's Cooldown when Rover enters the Dark Surge state by casting Heavy Attack Devastation.
In the Dark Surge state, Basic Attack 5 restores HP equal to 10% of total HP lost on hit.
Heavy Attack Devastation and Resonance Liberation Deadening Abyss reduces enemy's Havoc RES by 10% for 20s on hit.
In the Dark Surge state, Basic Attack 5 deals an additional Havoc DMG equal to 50% of Basic Attack 5 DMG.
In the Dark Surge state, Rover's Crit. Rate is increased by 25%.

Words.Title: Idle: II
Words.Content: This is a testament to my connection with the world around me, and it's very much my companion now, bearing witness to everything I've experienced on this journey.

Words.Title: Join Team: I
Words.Content: We still have a long journey ahead of us. Let's press on.

Words.Title: Join Team: III
Words.Content: Let me be there for everyone... As we head toward our shared future, leaving the past behind.

Words.Title: Ascension: I
Words.Content: The world around me... I can hear it clearer now.

Words.Title: Ascension: II
Words.Content: This power... it's mysterious, yet reassuring nonetheless.

Words.Title: Ascension: III
Words.Content: I still need more time to acquaint myself with this unfamiliar world.

Words.Title: Ascension: IV
Words.Content: A new journey awaits? Brimming with novel sounds, stories, and... fragmented memories.

Words.Title: Ascension: V
Words.Content: The place where the land ends is where the ocean begins. Our journey is far from ending.
